practitioner.about:
Dr. Riham Ismail is a Specialist Paediatrician qualified with  MBBCh and MD degrees. Dr. Riham has rich experience of dealing with newborn critical cases and resuscitation and good experience in paediatric emergency cases management and paediatric ICU.  

When Dr. Ismail has free time, she enjoys reading, swimming, and drawing. She can converse with her patients in Arabic and English.
